body_html:
Thanks Derek!

@recolgan, I'd be interested in knowing how much the recent changes (in the nightly build) help. Specifically, we merged a change that speeds up text -> float parsing significantly. I'm assuming you're reading float data? (assumption based on your defaults being [[]], which tf interprets as float32 if i'm not mistaken) What's num_cols_ in your case?
